"{\"uid\": \"buzzfeednews.com-article-leylamohammed-coco-gauff-supported-fans-controversial-olympic-defeat\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is been multiple times this year where that's happened to me - where I felt like I always have to be an advocate for myself on the court,\\\" said Coco.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BuzzFeed Staff  Coco was trailing 3-2 in the second set when her opponent, Donna, hit a service return that the line judge called out.\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\", \"score\": 0.9998729881515757, \"rank\": 0.0001270279824420587, \"text\": \"BuzzFeed\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\"}, {\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Freedman\", \"score\": 0.9907630462182788, \"rank\": 0.009316252478053856, \"text\": \"Donna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Freedman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Freedman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, Coco did not play the ball.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, chair umpire Jaume Campistol ruled the ball in and gave Donna the break point.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Freedman\", \"score\": 0.9907630462182788, \"rank\": 0.009316252478053856, \"text\": \"Donna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Freedman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Freedman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coco argued her case with the umpire for around five minutes, breaking down into tears at one point.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Avideoof the exchange shows the athlete telling Jaume, \\\"I never argue these calls.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But he called it out before I hit the ball.\\\"\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It always happens to me on this court,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I am getting cheated on constantly in this game,\\\" she said, adding, \\\"It happens to me; it happened toSerena [Williams].\\\"\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt that he called it before I hit, and I do not think the ref disagreed,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think he just thought it did not affect my swing, which I felt like it did.\\\"\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not going to sit here and say one point affected the result today because I was already on the losing side of things,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One personwroteon X, formerly Twitter, \\\"Coco Gauff is 100% correct that she has to advocate for herself on the court all the time.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 0.9999988738264367, \"rank\": 1.1261748383451055e-06, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They give unfair calls during the game and then apologize after the fact.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so proud to see her standing up for herself!\\\"\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Someone elseadded, \\\"Heartbreaking that Coco Gauff has to defend herself like this.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She deserves so much better.\\\"\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I was her I would be arguing and upset too if a judgement call is wrong.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not bash her for defending herself and standing up for what she believes,\\\"anotherperson wrote.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BuzzFeed Staff\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\", \"score\": 0.9998729881515757, \"rank\": 0.0001270279824420587, \"text\": \"BuzzFeed\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\"}]}]}"